title: Smart WiFi Solution 2.0 [EN-MULTI] Uploaded by MonstersBugle
description:
Smart WiFi Solution 2.0 [EN-MULTI] Uploaded by MonstersBugle

Program Version: 2.0 
Official website: link 
Language: English, Russian, Ukrainian 

Treatment: not required 

System requirements: 
Windows 7, Windows 8, Windows 10 

Description: 
The program for the transfer of WiFi settings (network name and password) on the new operating system. Run, do Export of profiles, reinstall Windows and import profiles. The operating system will automatically connect to the familiar WiFi network. 
Additional Information: 
What is the point of the program? Imagine the situation, you have brought a laptop to to reinstall Windows. Customers do not remember the password for your WiFi network (WiFi established staff ISP and the password is lost leaf). With this program, you can, after you reinstall the Windows, restore WiFi network profiles. Clients come home and the computer will connect to the familiar WiFi network, they do not have to re-configure the connection, or cause employees ISP. They will be pleasantly surprised by the fact that the new system is clean itself joined to WiFi. Your "rating" to grow with customers. You can learn about the availability of a new version of the program in the "About". The program does not process the data network, which is present in the title Cyrillic, such as "iPhone (Dmitry)." 

Features: 
Export profiles WiFi networks that connect computers; 
View details (the network name, password) WiFi networks; 
Import WiFi network profiles 

Changes: 
Version 2.0: 
Added function to send an error message; 
Changed the function of the "Data" button; 
Fixed some bugs. 

Version 1.1: 
Fixed a bug due to which the program is not processed in the network data containing the name of the sign "-"; 
Added ProgressBar; 
Slightly improved performance.
